{"tid":1654254,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"開始選舉新部署","createTime":"2019-10-14T13:42:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T15:14:44.000Z","uid":288563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"38a08dd2e97a2ddcdcb8d2ab428f936b1fc6c3b7","tid":1654254,"uid":288563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T13:42:35.000Z","msg":"報名泛民人士，開始被選擇主任，提出社交媒體上問題，即係今次區議會選舉，一定有大量候選人被DQ，你告佢就要兩年後先有結果，所以一定每區提名多人，尤其是素人，當正選被DQ時，有後備頂上，如果正選無DQ，後備就退選，只係罰萬幾蚊報名費，上次立法會選舉都用過，點都唔比票親中派，所以希望多些年輕素人，靜雞雞去報名，報名前取消所有社交網站，等選舉主任無把病係手，當正選被DQ後，才冒出頭來，當市民無得選正選時，一定選你。到時再由各巴絲打再發功，睇點樣係網上提供配票方法。"},{"pid":"78d4518bd73558ec502842592f9bcf9ca434f7c7","tid":1654254,"uid":283494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T13:56:30.000Z","msg":"推。"},{"pid":"bfb289337231d65efc6efe888784a0dfd4c9685d","tid":1654254,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T15:08:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">觀塘手足麻煩認住呢個女人！<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OwW9jJU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOwW9jJU.png&h=73f2a385&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2BZiXv5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2BZiXv5.png&h=a6c82315&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/16TLCwj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F16TLCwj.png&h=fa2d6f61&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dhCAfin.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdhCAfin.png&h=50c1e7a9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bfz3pbV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbfz3pbV.png&h=83e660b2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y8f94cf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy8f94cf.png&h=b75a44ef&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"50a540cccffc76eb66a95533f65d89ebd8